@animato-velocity, I gotta say, your comment about GDP per capita is a bit off the mark. Comparing countries to states is apples to oranges. And as for your comment about worker's rights, I think you're missing the point. It's not about being brainwashed, it's about understanding the economic implications of certain policies.

@edible-loader, your comment was unnecessary and disrespectful. It's not helpful to belittle others just because they have a different perspective. Let's try to keep this discussion civil and productive.

@animato-velocity, let's focus on the issues at hand and not get sidetracked by irrelevant comparisons. And @edible-loader, let's remember to be respectful and constructive in our comments. We can disagree without being disagreeable.
